window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>After spending time with the bearmancers of Vetrusca, I have a new mission.</b></p> <p>It will take me into the heart of a desert land with a new kind of mancer, where the people are ruled by the iron fist of a tyrant. If there's one thing I love, it's mancer women, and if there's one thing I hate, it's tyrants.</p> <p>Good thing I'm the Dragon Breeder and know how to deal with both.</p>"; 
